      • updateHungerStatus

        public void updateHungerStatus​()
        Update the hunger status of this.

        Updates are as following:

        1. Get the current time
        2. If this hunger status is FULL, check if the difference between hunger time and now is more than the maximum hungry duration. If yes, change this life status to DEAD
        3. If this hunger status is HUNGRY, check if the difference between full time and now is more than the maximum full duration. If yes, change this life status to HUNGRY and change the hunger time to now
        See Also:
        Hunger, StatusFish
